org.ecs.ecsbeekeeping.hive

Class Hive

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • org.ecs.ecsbeekeeping.hive.Hive

  • public class Hive
extends java.util.Observable
    A class to represent a Hive. Hives contain a number of Bee's and a store for three types of food: Honey, Royal Jelly and Pollen.
